data.description: Are you looking for a home in the Science Hill area with a lot of bedrooms, space and extra room to roam on your own 2.27 acres +/- look no further! This home boast of 4 bedrooms with an additional room (with no window) being used for a 5th bedroom. Not to mention in the walkout basement you will not only find additional bedrooms but a full kitchen, utility room and additional living room or game room! On the main level your will find your primary bedroom with its own attached room that would make for a great nursery or office! Next up you will find an additional bedroom, living room, dining room with doors leading out to your deck, kitchen area and a spot for a stackable washer and dryer if you so desire! This home is a great set up for having everything you need on both levels of the home! In addition to all of that you also have a detached garage/pole barn that is 30'x60' - 30'x48' is enclosed with a concrete floor, electric with 220 ready for your welder and you have 220 hookup for your camper under the attached 12'x30' lean-to. The home sits on approx. 1.87 ac +/- and is unrestricted - the lot that is included - approx. .40 ac+/- does have restrictions
